Journal Story: It is that season again!  I will be doing several sections this summer.  I am starting where I left off last year and heading north again!
We loved this campsite!  I would stay here again anytime!
It poured rain all night and the whole hike out in the morning!
I jumped  ahead to join a friend from  Tennessee.
Wildlife wanted to slack pack for the next few days, so we are parking  cars at each end of our day's hike.
Another beautiful day on  the trail with great  views!
